## 5. **USER INTERFACE DESIGN - IMPLEMENTED**

### **âœ… Completed Interface Components:**

#### **1. Home Page:**
- **Hero Section:** "SUPREME COURT CASES" title with animated gradient
- **Search Bar:** Centered with placeholder text and search button
- **Visual Design:** Professional legal aesthetics with blue/gold theme
- **Navigation:** Fixed header with logo and back navigation

#### **2. Search Results Page:**
- **Results Header:** Search query display and result count
- **Case Cards:** Grid layout with comprehensive case information
- **Empty States:** User-friendly messages for no results
- **Error Handling:** Clear error messages for API failures

#### **3. Case Detail Cards (Individual Components):**
- **Case Title:** Prominent display with date
- **Information Sections:**
  - Citation with bookmark icon
  - Court with building icon
  - Judges with users icon
  - Majority opinion with gavel icon
  - Source with book icon
  - Description with info icon (when available)
- **External Link:** "View Details" button to Wikidata

#### **4. Responsive Design:**
- **Mobile (< 768px):** Single column, optimized spacing
- **Tablet (768px-1024px):** Adaptive grid layout
- **Desktop (> 1024px):** Multi-column grid
- **Large Desktop (> 1400px):** Expanded layout

